{"tid":2091990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"清晨香港1位28歲的麥姓女子跳樓自殺死諫","createTime":"2020-07-03T03:44:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T04:36:32.000Z","uid":261647,"like":65,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"167b9ebe02628ee0a41cdef536d90b84f150af35","tid":2091990,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T03:44:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/m.ltn.tw/posts/2496562500429401\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fm.ltn.tw%2Fposts%2F2496562500429401&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBNMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=5eb143db\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/m.ltn.tw/posts/2496562500429401</a><br />\n<br />\n清晨香港1位28歲的麥姓女子，從一棟高樓上墜下，救護車抵達現場時便已身亡。<br />\n<br />\n1名香港網友在論壇上發文表示：「她（麥姓女子）同樣曾為反送中行動付出努力，每次示威行動都能見到她的身影。也許她對未來絕望了，在香港這個極權政府下，她看不到未來。我甚麼也幫不到，我能做的，只有代替她，完成餘下的抗爭。」<br />\n<br />\n該網友也發布了多張麥女留在床上的筆記，一邊放著相機、手機以及護目鏡。筆記中表示對於未來看不到希望，並且道歉，其中，也控訴香港警察死不認錯，「還沒到2047年香港就已經如此」。一旁的筆記上則是寫著：「不是民選的政府，是不會回應訴求的。香港需要的是革命。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2019/07/04/phpHVT5lS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2019%2F07%2F04%2FphpHVT5lS.png&h=e9e806e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港需要的是革命。"},{"pid":"2374f0c8c26e63e65c5393a2335383bd79c095b3","tid":2091990,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T03:47:57.000Z","msg":"⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯"},{"pid":"e44638232deb38d8f356fda36ed3baf39dc6e9f3","tid":2091990,"uid":237487,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T03:48:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n死黑警填命"},{"pid":"f03904789e3189e0bcea5572d484d9c5d8482b66","tid":2091990,"uid":237487,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T03:48:32.000Z","msg":"啲字好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1051cd996e162305dd915e671836057064db960","tid":2091990,"uid":11809,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T03:49:19.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"b9e7e6403ab0c30cd6e8d29f557d4fc670980251","tid":2091990,"uid":121197,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T03:50:55.000Z","msg":"一年了<br />\n死者嘅預言全部都成真"},{"pid":"ab87a30235a0175eddf9dbb1fd0568e5d6ef3c72","tid":2091990,"uid":252993,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T03:51:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cc4e5169cdb21d43408a494051cdde511da94a9","tid":2091990,"uid":59297,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T03:52:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7336f0ac824ddabb66f5e9d16b54d6a5008f6ed9","tid":2091990,"uid":73443,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T03:52:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c07fba19d377103889666f520abe808e5fdb7c9b","tid":2091990,"uid":244818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T03:52:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"492425a6ddbb1c8e5e9581b2b823c3d58f4de6b6","tid":2091990,"uid":189157,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T03:53:08.000Z","msg":"剩低既人<br />\n要留返條命啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"195df889a1f0fc9f72a3b8852a